&lt;li&gt;Friendly and inclusive workplace culture &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Benefits and Growth listed above may vary based on the country of your employment and the&amp;nbsp;nature of your employment with Datadog.&lt;/p&gt;
